title: United Kingdom Imports - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical Plants
description: Imports - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical Plants in the United Kingdom decreased to 124.79 GBP Million in September from 125.09 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical P in the United Kingdom averaged 57.56 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 271.26 GBP Million in February of 2022 and a record low of 16.35 GBP Million in April of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Oil Seeds & Oleaginous Fruits, Medical.
